headline: Is Eaton’s Valuation Still Justified After Its Huge Multi Year Share Price Surge?
summary: Wondering if Eaton at around $323 a share is still a smart buy or if the big gains are already behind it? This article is going to unpack what the current price really implies about its value. The stock has dipped slightly in the short term, with returns of 2.5% over the last week but -2.0% over the last month and -2.5% year to date.
